# 🏛️ Temple Financial Management System — Architecture Overview

> Designed for rapid SWE onboarding. Covers stack, modules, data models, API surface, and key business logic flows.

---

## 1. High-Level System Architecture

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Browser["🌐 Browser (Port 5173)"]
        FE["React + Vite + Tailwind v4\nfrontend/"]
    end

    subgraph API["🖥️ Node.js Express Server (Port 3001)"]
        IDX["index.js\nEntry Point + CORS + Router"]
        subgraph Modules["modules/"]
            TXN["transaction/routes.js"]
            PAY["payroll/routes.js"]
            QUO["quotes/routes.js"]
            INV["invoices/routes.js"]
            RPT["reports/routes.js"]
        end
        LIB["lib/prisma.js\nSingleton Client"]
    end

    subgraph DB["🗄️ Data Layer"]
        PRI["Prisma ORM\nprisma/schema.prisma"]
        SQLite["SQLite\ndev.db"]
    end

    FE -->|"axios HTTP calls\n/api/*"| IDX
    IDX --> TXN
    IDX --> PAY
    IDX --> QUO
    IDX --> INV
    IDX --> RPT
    TXN --> LIB
    PAY --> LIB
    QUO --> LIB
    INV --> LIB
    RPT --> LIB
    LIB --> PRI
    PRI --> SQLite
```

