## 3. Backend Module Map & REST API Endpoints

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph "Express Router — /api"
        subgraph TX["📋 /transactions"]
            TX1["GET / — list (filter: type, category, date)"]
            TX2["GET /:id — single"]
            TX3["POST / — create"]
            TX4["PUT /:id — update"]
            TX5["DELETE /:id — soft delete"]
            TX6["GET /stats/summary — totals"]
        end

        subgraph PY["💰 /payroll"]
            PY1["GET / — list (filter: status, payPeriod)"]
            PY2["GET /:id — single"]
            PY3["POST / — create entry"]
            PY4["PUT /:id — update entry"]
            PY5["POST /:id/pay — 🔀 pay & auto-create Tx"]
            PY6["DELETE /:id — soft delete"]
        end

        subgraph QU["📄 /quotes"]
            QU1["GET / — list (filter: status)"]
            QU2["GET /:id — single"]
            QU3["POST / — create"]
            QU4["PUT /:id — update / change status"]
            QU5["POST /:id/convert — 🔀 convert to Invoice"]
            QU6["DELETE /:id — soft delete"]
        end

        subgraph IN["🧾 /invoices"]
            IN1["GET / — list (filter: status)"]
            IN2["GET /:id — single"]
            IN3["POST / — create standalone"]
            IN4["PUT /:id — update"]
            IN5["POST /:id/pay — 🔀 pay & auto-create Tx"]
            IN6["DELETE /:id — soft delete"]
        end

        subgraph RP["📊 /reports"]
            RP1["GET /dashboard — KPI summary + monthly chart data"]
            RP2["GET /snapshots — list profit snapshots"]
            RP3["POST /snapshots — create period snapshot"]
            RP4["GET /income-expense — filtered P&L report"]
        end
    end
```

> 🔀 = **automated cross-module side-effect** (see Business Logic section below)

