## 9. Module Ownership Quick-Reference

| Module | File | Key Special Endpoint | Side Effect |
|---|---|---|---|
| Transactions | [modules/transaction/routes.js](file:///home/jchang/Projects/AhChang/temple-finance/backend/modules/transaction/routes.js) | `GET /stats/summary` | None (source of truth) |
| Payroll | [modules/payroll/routes.js](file:///home/jchang/Projects/AhChang/temple-finance/backend/modules/payroll/routes.js) | `POST /:id/pay` | Creates `Transaction` (expense) |
| Quotes | [modules/quotes/routes.js](file:///home/jchang/Projects/AhChang/temple-finance/backend/modules/quotes/routes.js) | `POST /:id/convert` | Creates `Invoice` record |
| Invoices | [modules/invoices/routes.js](file:///home/jchang/Projects/AhChang/temple-finance/backend/modules/invoices/routes.js) | `POST /:id/pay` | Creates `Transaction` (income) |
| Reports | [modules/reports/routes.js](file:///home/jchang/Projects/AhChang/temple-finance/backend/modules/reports/routes.js) | `GET /dashboard` | Read-only aggregation |
| DB Lib | `lib/prisma.js` | — | Singleton Prisma client |
